Chavez Says He May Expropriate Food Distributors That ‘Hoard’

-- B y   C o r i n a   R o d r i g u e z   P o n s   a n d   J o s e   O r o z c o
-- 
2011-05-15T18:03:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-15/chavez-says-he-may-expropriate-food-distributors-that-hoard-.html
Venezuelan President  Hugo Chavez ,
speaking on state television, said his government could
expropriate food distributors that are found to be hoarding
products.  To contact the reporter on this story:
